These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
The people have 2 different hobbies: photography, dancing
The people have 2 different jobs:  software-developer, dressmaker
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: rowing, rugby
The people use 2 different means of transport: subway, tram
1. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far right##1
2. the person who's sport is rowing is on the right of the person driving the tram##1
3. the software-developer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Hobby       | dancing       | photography |
| Job         | dressmaker | software-developer  |
| Sport       | rugby    | rowing    |
| Transport   | tram       | subway      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, mirinda
The people have 2 different jobs:  analyst, designer
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: romance, comedy
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: volleyball, handball
1. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1
2. the analyst is on the far left##1
3. the person watching romance movies is on the right of the person drinking mirinda##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | mirinda     | juice |
| Job           | analyst | designer      |
| Movie-Genre   | comedy  | romance      |
| Sport         | volleyball | handball     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: milk, water
There 2 different types of food: radish, pear
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, indie
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, motorbike
1. the fan of indie is on the left of the person drinking water##1
2. the person drinking milk is the person driving the motorbike##1
3. the person eating radish is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | milk | water  |
| Food          | radish    | pear   |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | trance   |
| Transport     | motorbike     | jet-ski |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
