There 2 different types of food: cabbage, broccoli
The people have 2 different jobs:  project-manager, fisherman
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: trance, dubstep
1. the fan of trance is on the far left##1
2. the project-manager is on the right of the person drinking coffee##1
3. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person eating cabbage##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Beverage      | coffee       | hot-chocolate |
| Food          | broccoli         | cabbage    |
| Job           | fisherman | project-manager    |
| Music-Genre   | trance           | dubstep   |

