The people prefer 2 different music-genres: soul, rock
There are 2 different nationalities: pakistani, french
2 different pets are kept: hamster, pony
1. the french is the owner of the pony##1
2. the fan of rock is on the right of the person eating pepper##1
3. the french is on the right of the owner of the hamster##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |
| Food          | pepper | kale |
| Music-Genre   | soul     | rock      |
| Nationality   | pakistani | french    |
| Pet           | hamster    | pony    |

